It is soo cold..

Yeah..anyways..I just went to Taco Johns..and sat in line for like 30 minutes because the lady in front of us kept ordering more. I am surprised they had any food left by the time that lady was done ordering. Stupid people. Anyways, we have to do this poetry project for Mr. Pack, and its due like Tuesday or Wednesday, but I have practice every day next week and I will have NO time to do it, so I did it all today, yeah..12 poems. And I finished. yay. They are kinda retarded..but oh well.

I woke up at 12 today. It felt so good to sleep late. I was super excited. Considering the fact I woke up at 5 in the morning yesterday to go shopping, and you know what I left with. Exactly, Nothing. Yeah, how depressing, oh well..you don't always get what you want :-/   .

I have a stye(spelling) and an eye infection in my left eye. How fun. It hurts like crap, but I'll be ok. I can't believe its almost christmas..how great! I love christmas..it's awesome.

Well, I think i've bored you all with enough..so, I am out.

?tnemmoc?

<3..*Morgan Elizabeth*..<3

Ok! It has been *FOREVER* since ive updated, but hey..who cares, right? Yeah..I've been reading everyones, and i was like..hey, I'll update. Guys..I had the best weekend the other day..went and seen Chucky..which was a great movie..and went to an AWESOME party..and danced a lot!! considering the fact that i love to dance more than anything..and i have a cheerleading competition december 3-5..which is..NEXT WEEKEND! ahhhhhhhh! yeah..im excited though..but I dont know whats wrong with me..i'm never happy anymore..i'm not doing good in math at all..which is weird because i always make ok grades..and im not doing so well..and i just i dont know..im always tired..and i just never feel like doing anything anymore..but..oh well? I'm going to go..thgin doog..



evol syawla,

Ok, well I havnt updated in here in a while. Probably because im getting so damn tired of that lame ass who keeps commenting. Why dont you grow up, and if you're going to comment..be man enough to put your damn name. 

Anyways...what have I done lately? Well, absolutely nothing! I cant wait till' the West & East game..its gonna be awesome. Yay. It feels like sunday to me, but its only saturday..hm..weird. We started reading Romeo and Juliet in English. How sweet..I love that story. yay.

Gym is awesome, maybe its just awesome because the people in there are awesome. Its great. We played like badmitten or somethin..it was hard..but it was soo fun! Yay. I didnt wake up until 12:30 today..it was awesome to sleep late.

Well, I am going to go, because I have nothing else to write!


<3 always

Morgan*

Well today was okay. I went to school and had a pretty good day, so it was cool. Came home and did all my homework, except I still have to study for my quiz in Health Science tomorrow. What fun!.! I am so fed up with some people, mostly the kid who keeps commenting. Thanks for whoever is doing it. You are so annoying. Grow up, and get a life! 

I went the mall a second ago, I found a lot of things I really like!! I am getting this Nike gym bag tomorrow! Yay! I am so excited, its pink and it's so cute. It looks like a mini backpack! WooHoo! Tiffany is supposed to be getting this one. Its really cute too, but I am obsessed with Pink! So yeah..I like the pink one! He he! Oh yeah, I found me some converses too, they are pink and black. They are awesome! But, I think I may wait and see if I can find me some army ones. I like them better. But oh well, you can't always have what you want. :-(


I walked when I got home, just me and mom. It was fun, but now I am tired, and I still have to study. fun, huh? So, I am going to go, and I am sure I'll have some comment put in here by that lame ass who needs to grow up!!

<3 yall!

*Morgan*

OK, well let's start off with last night. I think last night was the most interesting night I've had in a while.Some of it was good, and most of it was bad. Well, first of all, me and Jimmy made up, so I'm glad, because we got into like a horrible fight, and when i say horrible, im not joking. I love you Jimmy! Well, me and Tiff went to the movies last night, and seen cookout, turns out, we left early to go walking around, b/c it was the dumbest movie ive ever seen. Well, I got home, checked my comments. And there was the start of my bad night. I'm not even going to say what was in it, so..don't ask. That really made my day whoever did that. Thank you. After that was pretty okay.

I think I'm going to Tiffany's house after she gets home from 7&6 thing. Woohoo. I love the Tiffany

Well, I am going to go...I'll talk to you  crazy kids later!

<3 always..

Well guys. Let's start off by telling you my progress reports. Tee Hee. Gym-100 Math-85 Health Science-84 English-87(Which is really good for all the classes I have). So I'm very happy. I beat Tiffany in Health Science, ha ha ha! I love her though. Even though she sucks at Health Science, wait, I think EVERYONE does. Who cares. Tiffany came home with me today. We went to the mall and got pizza with my Mamaw. Then I went to Peircing Pagoda, and had a crazy idea I wanted the top of my ear peirced again. So my mamaw was like oh gosh, Morgan, I have to sign all these papers, what if something happens and your mom sues me. I was like Mamaw, it's not like my ear is going to fall off. I least I hope it won't! Ha Ha. So yeah, I got it peirced, and it hurt like 2 seconds, and it's fine now. Tiff was going to get hers done if she would have had money. I am going to take her one day and get it done. He He. I think it's really cute though. So, I am  happy.
   We went to the Freshman game, which was really boring, but me and Tiffany have fun wherever we go. Ha Ha. It was cool. We took her to SunTrust to meet her Daddy. Then I came home and did my stupid Math homework! Fun. Then I studied for my "Antigone" test tomorrow, which is supposed to be really hard. Wait, EVERYTHING is hard in Pack's class though. You can't help but love the old man though. He's a great teacher, considering the fact me and Kristen learned NOTHING in Mrs. Isom's class last year. Thanks Mrs. Isom. My class is awesome. Jake, Patrick, Jordan, and me always cut up. It's fun. I have a project due in there on Monday. Thank goodness it's not a big one. 
   So here I am, with all my homework done, and nothing to do. So, I am going to go over here and chill. IM me on AIM if you want to.

Comment. They make me smile :-)
<3 /\/\organ**
http://alilmocheers22.livejournal.com/1537.html

Hm. What so say. Oh, yes. Well I got to school, went and talked to all my friends outside before school starts, because thats the best time to talk to everybody. Went to gym, then me and Keela went walking around. It was fun. Then we went back to gym when the bell rang. WooHoo. We played like Eclipse Ball, or somethin. It was cool. Went to math, Mr. King told Julia if she shot the peice of paper in the trash can, we wouldn't have homework, so we all didn't get our hopes up, because she sucks and making shots. AMAZINGLY, she made it! WooHoo, Go Julia! So I had no homework in math. Then, the dreadful class Health Science, went in there, found out we had a quiz in which MORGAN had known NOTHING about. It's all good though. I don't think I did too bad. Then I went to my favorite class ever! PACK'S class. Yes, I do admit he's pretty cool. We finished "Antigone" which was an AWESOME story, considering the fact I love greek drama. The ending was sad though. Tear. We get to read another greek story. WooHoo. I hope it's ending is better than the last one. Well, that was my day.
  Lets talk about something other than school, because I've rambled on enough about it. I think me and Tiff are going to the Freshman game tomorrow night. Not sure though. I went to Subway a few minutes ago. It was awesome! I love subway, and I havn't had it in forever. Woohoo. Go me. 
  I really wish it would stop raining. It is so depressing. I want to go outside, and jump on the trampoline, but no, just because of stupid tropical storm "FRANCES" Ha. Ha. I hate storms, they don't scare me, they are just boring. We get progress reports tomorrow. Holy crap. I think I did really good in all my classes except one. Which I'm sure you all can guess. Well if not, let me help you. HEALTH SCIENCE. It is like the most BORING class in the WHOLE entire WORLD. But, everyones doing bad, so it's not that bad for me. He. He.
  Have you all noticed that there is like nothing to do in Morristown these days. Hm, they need to get some new restaurants too. I eat at like the same place every week. We need something good, something like my FAVORITE place in the world. RED LOBSTER!! Mmm, I love seafood, and guess what. . .we have nothing but Long Johns, and Captain Dees. Dude, that is not Seafood, thats like FAKE!
  Well, I think I've put enough in here, so I'm going to go get me somethin to snack on, and watch me a lil' TV. Yall have a good night, and be good!

**Leave comments, they make me smile!** :-)
<3..*..morgan~elizabeth..*..<3

Man, it's like 11:51 and I am so tired! We didn't have school today! Yes! I get to go shopping in West Town :-) !! I have got to get me some new shirts, I desperately need some. I think I get to eat at my favorite place in the WHOLE wide world!! ReD lObStEr!!!! Yay!

  Well, I convinced Tiffany to get a LiveJournal, and she got one. Yay. They are really good to write in, because it helps you releave some crap off of yourself. I want the top of my ear peirced again. It was so cute. Blah. Im so bored.

  I can't believe the long weekend is like already almost over. That sucks.

  School, hows school. I actually like it, excepting the fact that we have butt-loads of homework. And Im not exaggerating. Pack's class is awesome, if we didnt have all the homework. But the people in there are awesome. It's fun. Me and Tiffany have Health Science together. And I believe I would die in there if I didnt have her. Its like all seniors and juniors and crap. Blah

  Well. I am going to go now! I hope yall have a wonderful Labor day!!

  Leave comments they make me smile!

Wow, what an interesting day. Also, what a boring day it was. We are so off of school tomorrow! Yes! The VOLS game was so awesome! We did really great. I wish I could have gone to the game though. But watching it on TV was ok! My brother left a few minutes ago, AGAIN. Lol. I just love him. Me and Ashley jumped on the trampoline today, I taught her a few tricks. She actually did them. Lol! I love her to death. Shes great. So, I've come to the point that I have few friends. Which doesn't bother me, because I dont like having to put up with all kinds of drama. Tiffany is so great. I love her to death, and shes been through alot. Shes an awesome person to talk to.

 Hm, what else. I got some Vols chapstick today. Hehe. Its awesome. I did have another LiveJournal, but I got a virus in my computer, and we lost everything, Including our pictures from  CHRISTMAS. It sucked. Its kinda cold in here. Speaking of Christmas, it's not too far away! WooHoo! I love Christmas.

  There is like, nothing else to talk about. So! By that, I am going to go over here and find something to do! Hope yall have a great night and a great Labor Day!! Because I get to go shopping! YES!! Love you guys soo much!

  Leave comments, they really make me smile!
